      <title>巴基斯坦的通货膨胀率在3月的1％以下的新鲜低下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/pakistan-s-inflation-eases-to-a-fresh-low-below-1-in-march</link>
