    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税威胁需求和经济，商品袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/commodities-hit-as-trump-s-tariffs-threaten-demand-and-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于唐纳德·特朗普总统对猛烈抨击的猛烈抨击，石油从工业金属到谷物的其他商品跌至谷物，这造成了一场贸易战，威胁着损害全球经济和对原材料的需求。黄金在早些时候取得了新的纪录后跌落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/commodities-hit-as-trump-s-tariffs-threaten-demand-and-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 08:57:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴市场投资者为美国关税提供“身体打击”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/asia-currencies-stocks-lead-emerging-peers-lower-amid-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统宣布对出口驱动的国家的高关税之后，整个发展中国家的资产跌跌撞撞，最小，最弱的经济体针对中国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/asia-currencies-stocks-lead-emerging-peers-lower-amid-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 06:44:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
